@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
skinparam responseMessageColor #2e7d32

participant "Application Controller" as App
participant "AI Service Orchestrator" as AI
participant "LLM & Verification Logic" as Logic

note over AI, Logic: Each phase produces a specific JSON schema output

== Phase 1: Company Context ==
App -> AI : Start Phase 1 (Job Data, Profile)
activate AI
AI -> Logic : Analyze company background
Logic --> AI : Context Data
AI --> App : **JSON Response:** { "company_info": { "name", "vibe", "location"... } }
deactivate AI

== Phase 2: Requirements ==
App -> AI : Start Phase 2 (Context + Job Post)
activate AI
AI -> Logic : Extract & Verify requirements
Logic --> AI : Validated Requirements
AI --> App : **JSON Response:** { "requirements": [ { "id", "description", "priority" } ] }
deactivate AI

== Phase 3: Candidate Evidence ==
App -> AI : Start Phase 3 (Requirements + Files)
activate AI
AI -> Logic : Find evidence & Check citations
Logic --> AI : Evidence Map
AI --> App : **JSON Response:** { "evidence": [ { "requirement_id", "proof", "source_file" } ] }
deactivate AI

== Phase 4: Matching ==
App -> AI : Start Phase 4 (Requirements + Evidence)
activate AI
AI -> Logic : Evaluate match strength
Logic --> AI : Match Analysis
AI --> App : **JSON Response:** { "match_score": 0.85, "analysis": { "strengths", "gaps" } }
deactivate AI

== Phase 5: Application Generation ==
App -> AI : Start Phase 5 (All Data + Preferences)
activate AI
AI -> Logic : Draft text & Verify layout
Logic --> AI : Final Document
AI --> App : **JSON Response:** { "application": { "content", "metadata", "layout_status" } }
deactivate AI

@enduml